"{\"uid\": \"jamaicaobserver.com-2024-06-28-france-makes-multibillion-euro-gamble-olympic-gold\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"PARIS, France (AFP) - The Paris Olympics are set to cost almost nine billion euros according to the latest estimates and the impact on the economy is likely to be more \\\"psychological\\\" than financial.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 199, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7, \"end\": 13, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999894004465802, \"rank\": 5.027372808648703e-06, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"PARIS\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 5}, {\"ngram\": \"AFP\", \"from\": 15, \"to\": 18}, {\"ngram\": \"The Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 22, \"to\": 40}, {\"ngram\": \"almost nine billion euros\", \"from\": 57, \"to\": 82}, {\"ngram\": \"the latest estimates\", \"from\": 96, \"to\": 116}, {\"ngram\": \"the impact\", \"from\": 121, \"to\": 131}, {\"ngram\": \"the economy\", \"from\": 135, \"to\": 146}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ahead of the July 26 opening ceremony, ministers and observers are juggling the figures to estimate the costs and benefits of the sporting spectacle.\", \"from\": 201, \"to\": 350, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the July 26 opening ceremony\", \"from\": 210, \"to\": 238}, {\"ngram\": \"ministers\", \"from\": 240, \"to\": 249}, {\"ngram\": \"observers\", \"from\": 254, \"to\": 263}, {\"ngram\": \"the figures\", \"from\": 277, \"to\": 288}, {\"ngram\": \"the costs\", \"from\": 301, \"to\": 310}, {\"ngram\": \"benefits\", \"from\": 315, \"to\": 323}, {\"ngram\": \"the sporting spectacle\", \"from\": 327, \"to\": 349}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So far, French authorities are predicting an overall cost - shared between the state and organisers - of nearly nine billion euros ($9.5 billion), although the official figure will take time to firm up.\", \"from\": 352, \"to\": 554, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 360, \"end\": 366, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9701466397885914, \"rank\": 0.02765349750455449, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the state\", \"from\": 427, \"to\": 436}, {\"ngram\": \"organisers\", \"from\": 441, \"to\": 451}, {\"ngram\": \"nearly nine billion euros\", \"from\": 457, \"to\": 482}, {\"ngram\": \"the official figure\", \"from\": 508, \"to\": 527}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 538, \"to\": 542}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Costs are always difficult to predict or confirm.\", \"from\": 556, \"to\": 605, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Costs\", \"from\": 556, \"to\": 561}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Tokyo Olympics, delayed for a year until 2021 because of Covid-19, cost about $12.9 billion, Japan's Audit Board has been reported as saying.\", \"from\": 607, \"to\": 752, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 704, \"end\": 709, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Economy_of_Japan\", \"score\": 0.999999999006377, \"rank\": 9.936611923686993e-10, \"text\": \"Japan\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Economy_of_Japan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Economy_of_Japan\"}, {\"begin\": 712, \"end\": 723, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Audit_Board_of_Indonesia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Audit Board\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q327333\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Audit_Board_of_Indonesia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Audit_Board_of_Indonesia\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Tokyo Olympics\", \"from\": 607, \"to\": 625}, {\"ngram\": \"a year\", \"from\": 639, \"to\": 645}, {\"ngram\": \"Covid-19\", \"from\": 668, \"to\": 676}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Greece's finance ministry estimates that the 2004 Athens Games cost $9.1 billion - although some independent estimates are closer to $15 billion.\", \"from\": 754, \"to\": 899, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 754, \"end\": 760, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greek_government-debt_crisis\", \"score\": 0.9999999998603926, \"rank\": 1.3971251773833733e-10, \"text\": \"Greece\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greek_government-debt_crisis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greek_government-debt_crisis\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 2004 Athens Games\", \"from\": 795, \"to\": 816}, {\"ngram\": \"some independent estimates\", \"from\": 846, \"to\": 872}]}, {\"sentence\": \"London 2012 cost up to $15 billion.\", \"from\": 900, \"to\": 935, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 900, \"end\": 911, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999987984959203, \"rank\": 1.1229698642050455e-06, \"text\": \"London 2012\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Paris organising committee, financed by ticket sales, sponsors and International Olympic Committee (IOC) funds, has a budget of about 4.4 billion euros and has a mantra of \\\"the Games finance the Games.\\\"\", \"from\": 937, \"to\": 1143, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 941, \"end\": 946, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999181455, \"rank\": 8.199095851213292e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"ticket sales\", \"from\": 981, \"to\": 993}, {\"ngram\": \"sponsors\", \"from\": 995, \"to\": 1003}, {\"ngram\": \"IOC\", \"from\": 1041, \"to\": 1044}, {\"ngram\": \"a budget\", \"from\": 1057, \"to\": 1065}, {\"ngram\": \"about 4.4 billion euros\", \"from\": 1069, \"to\": 1092}, {\"ngram\": \"a mantra\", \"from\": 1101, \"to\": 1109}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 1114, \"to\": 1123}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 1132, \"to\": 1141}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But billions of euros of public money have also gone into the Solideo infrastructure group that has built the Olympic village north of the French capital and other facilities.\", \"from\": 1145, \"to\": 1320, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1284, \"end\": 1290, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9701466397885914, \"rank\": 0.02765349750455449, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"billions\", \"from\": 1149, \"to\": 1157}, {\"ngram\": \"euros\", \"from\": 1161, \"to\": 1166}, {\"ngram\": \"public money\", \"from\": 1170, \"to\": 1182}, {\"ngram\": \"the Solideo infrastructure group\", \"from\": 1203, \"to\": 1235}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic village\", \"from\": 1251, \"to\": 1270}, {\"ngram\": \"other facilities\", \"from\": 1303, \"to\": 1319}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The final bill will depend on the amount of spending on Olympic bonuses for metro drivers, police and emergency services, as well as the general cost of security.\", \"from\": 1322, \"to\": 1484, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The final bill\", \"from\": 1322, \"to\": 1336}, {\"ngram\": \"the amount\", \"from\": 1352, \"to\": 1362}, {\"ngram\": \"spending\", \"from\": 1366, \"to\": 1374}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic bonuses\", \"from\": 1378, \"to\": 1393}, {\"ngram\": \"metro drivers\", \"from\": 1398, \"to\": 1411}, {\"ngram\": \"police\", \"from\": 1413, \"to\": 1419}, {\"ngram\": \"emergency services\", \"from\": 1424, \"to\": 1442}, {\"ngram\": \"the general cost\", \"from\": 1455, \"to\": 1471}, {\"ngram\": \"security\", \"from\": 1475, \"to\": 1483}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The government this week alloted another 33 million euros to Paralympics organisers who are struggling with ticket sales.\", \"from\": 1486, \"to\": 1607, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The government\", \"from\": 1486, \"to\": 1500}, {\"ngram\": \"another 33 million euros\", \"from\": 1519, \"to\": 1543}, {\"ngram\": \"Paralympics organisers\", \"from\": 1547, \"to\": 1569}, {\"ngram\": \"ticket sales\", \"from\": 1594, \"to\": 1606}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The government and local authorities have so far committed about 2.4 billion euros to the Paris Olympics, mainly for construction.\", \"from\": 1609, \"to\": 1739, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1699, \"end\": 1713, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The government and local authorities\", \"from\": 1609, \"to\": 1645}, {\"ngram\": \"about 2.4 billion euros\", \"from\": 1668, \"to\": 1691}, {\"ngram\": \"construction\", \"from\": 1726, \"to\": 1738}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But the head of the government's Court of Accounts has estimated that the final state cost could be up to five billion euros.\", \"from\": 1741, \"to\": 1866, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the head\", \"from\": 1745, \"to\": 1753}, {\"ngram\": \"the government's Court\", \"from\": 1757, \"to\": 1779}, {\"ngram\": \"Accounts\", \"from\": 1783, \"to\": 1791}, {\"ngram\": \"the final state cost\", \"from\": 1811, \"to\": 1831}, {\"ngram\": \"up to five billion euros\", \"from\": 1841, \"to\": 1865}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Bruno Cavalier, chief economist for Oddo BHF financial services group, said the \\\"direct state involvement is relatively limited\\\".\", \"from\": 1868, \"to\": 1997, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1874, \"end\": 1882, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vauxhall_Cavalier\", \"score\": 0.7956351883569937, \"rank\": 0.2557322939153395, \"text\": \"Cavalier\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vauxhall_Cavalier\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vauxhall_Cavalier\"}, {\"begin\": 1904, \"end\": 1912, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ODDO_BHF\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Oddo BHF\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ODDO_BHF\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ODDO_BHF\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"chief economist\", \"from\": 1884, \"to\": 1899}, {\"ngram\": \"the \\\"direct state involvement\", \"from\": 1944, \"to\": 1973}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He added that the Olympics will not \\\"radically change\\\" France's public debt of about $3.2 trillion.\", \"from\": 1998, \"to\": 2097, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2053, \"end\": 2059, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999894004465802, \"rank\": 5.027372808648703e-06, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 2012, \"to\": 2024}]}, {\"sentence\": \"According to the Centre for Law and Economy of Sport (CDES), which has been monitoring the Paris Games for the IOC and the Paris 2024 organisers, the event will produce between 6.7 billion and 11.1 billion euros in economic benefits for the Paris region.\", \"from\": 2099, \"to\": 2353, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2210, \"end\": 2213, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 0.9999999999736247, \"rank\": 2.6428505689856923e-11, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 2222, \"end\": 2232, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.5771221918444514e-20, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 2340, \"end\": 2345, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999181455, \"rank\": 8.199095851213292e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Centre\", \"from\": 2112, \"to\": 2122}, {\"ngram\": \"Law\", \"from\": 2127, \"to\": 2130}, {\"ngram\": \"Economy\", \"from\": 2135, \"to\": 2142}, {\"ngram\": \"Sport\", \"from\": 2146, \"to\": 2151}, {\"ngram\": \"CDES\", \"from\": 2153, \"to\": 2157}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Games\", \"from\": 2186, \"to\": 2201}, {\"ngram\": \"the event\", \"from\": 2245, \"to\": 2254}, {\"ngram\": \"11.1 billion euros\", \"from\": 2292, \"to\": 2310}, {\"ngram\": \"economic benefits\", \"from\": 2314, \"to\": 2331}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But it added that these benefits would be spread over 20 years.\", \"from\": 2355, \"to\": 2418, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"these benefits\", \"from\": 2373, \"to\": 2387}, {\"ngram\": \"20 years\", \"from\": 2409, \"to\": 2417}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In February, the Asteres consultancy estimated that the Games would bring in 5.3 billion euros in extra tax and social revenues.\", \"from\": 2420, \"to\": 2548, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"February\", \"from\": 2423, \"to\": 2431}, {\"ngram\": \"the Asteres consultancy\", \"from\": 2433, \"to\": 2456}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 2472, \"to\": 2481}, {\"ngram\": \"5.3 billion euros\", \"from\": 2497, \"to\": 2514}, {\"ngram\": \"extra tax and social revenues\", \"from\": 2518, \"to\": 2547}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Deutsche Bank said in a study this month that \\\"host nations of the Olympics or FIFA World Cups rarely earn positive economic or even social returns on what are often massive and publicly-funded investment sprees on new stadiums and public infrastructure.\\\"\", \"from\": 2550, \"to\": 2805, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2550, \"end\": 2563, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Deutsche_Bank\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.945470692481435e-46, \"text\": \"Deutsche Bank\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Deutsche_Bank\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Deutsche_Bank\"}, {\"begin\": 2629, \"end\": 2633, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FIFA\", \"score\": 0.9999999979568202, \"rank\": 2.0394303442370058e-09, \"text\": \"FIFA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FIFA\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FIFA\"}, {\"begin\": 2634, \"end\": 2644, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FIFA_World_Cup\", \"score\": 0.9983398074689088, \"rank\": 0.001452450448631645, \"text\": \"World Cups\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FIFA_World_Cup\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FIFA_World_Cup\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a study\", \"from\": 2572, \"to\": 2579}, {\"ngram\": \"host nations\", \"from\": 2597, \"to\": 2609}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 2613, \"to\": 2625}, {\"ngram\": \"positive economic or even social returns\", \"from\": 2657, \"to\": 2697}, {\"ngram\": \"massive and publicly-funded investment sprees\", \"from\": 2716, \"to\": 2761}, {\"ngram\": \"new stadiums\", \"from\": 2765, \"to\": 2777}, {\"ngram\": \"public infrastructure\", \"from\": 2782, \"to\": 2803}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It said that even the short-term boost to investment and employment was \\\"limited\\\" unless the host country is going through a recession.\", \"from\": 2807, \"to\": 2942, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"even the short-term boost\", \"from\": 2820, \"to\": 2845}, {\"ngram\": \"investment\", \"from\": 2849, \"to\": 2859}, {\"ngram\": \"employment\", \"from\": 2864, \"to\": 2874}, {\"ngram\": \"the host country\", \"from\": 2896, \"to\": 2912}, {\"ngram\": \"a recession\", \"from\": 2930, \"to\": 2941}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For Bank of France governor Francois Villeroy de Galhau, the Paris Olympics will have more of a \\\"psychological\\\" impact than economic.\", \"from\": 2944, \"to\": 3077, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"France\", \"from\": 2956, \"to\": 2962}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 3001, \"to\": 3019}, {\"ngram\": \"a \\\"psychological\\\" impact\", \"from\": 3038, \"to\": 3062}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But he said if France can improve its image around the world through the Games, then it could eventually expect new investment.\", \"from\": 3079, \"to\": 3206, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3094, \"end\": 3100, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999894004465802, \"rank\": 5.027372808648703e-06, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"its image\", \"from\": 3113, \"to\": 3122}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 3130, \"to\": 3139}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 3148, \"to\": 3157}, {\"ngram\": \"new investment\", \"from\": 3191, \"to\": 3205}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the short-term some companies are already seeking to cash in.\", \"from\": 3208, \"to\": 3272, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the short-term some companies\", \"from\": 3211, \"to\": 3240}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Le Slip Francais, an underwear maker, is making thousands of extra underpants, swimming costumes, pyjamas and other goods in the Olympic colours, according to its managing director Lea Marie.\", \"from\": 3274, \"to\": 3465, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3455, \"end\": 3458, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/River_Lea\", \"score\": 0.9955691171626891, \"rank\": 0.004450602934594016, \"text\": \"Lea\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/River_Lea\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/River_Lea\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Le Slip Francais\", \"from\": 3274, \"to\": 3290}, {\"ngram\": \"an underwear maker\", \"from\": 3292, \"to\": 3310}, {\"ngram\": \"thousands\", \"from\": 3322, \"to\": 3331}, {\"ngram\": \"extra underpants\", \"from\": 3335, \"to\": 3351}, {\"ngram\": \"swimming costumes\", \"from\": 3353, \"to\": 3370}, {\"ngram\": \"pyjamas\", \"from\": 3372, \"to\": 3379}, {\"ngram\": \"other goods\", \"from\": 3384, \"to\": 3395}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic colours\", \"from\": 3399, \"to\": 3418}, {\"ngram\": \"its managing director\", \"from\": 3433, \"to\": 3454}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It has created work in our factories\\\" and for the company's 80 sub-contractors, she said.\", \"from\": 3467, \"to\": 3557, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"work\", \"from\": 3483, \"to\": 3487}, {\"ngram\": \"our factories\", \"from\": 3491, \"to\": 3504}, {\"ngram\": \"the company's 80 sub\", \"from\": 3514, \"to\": 3534}, {\"ngram\": \"contractors\", \"from\": 3535, \"to\": 3546}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Companies linked to the Olympic building spree have also benefited.\", \"from\": 3559, \"to\": 3626, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Companies\", \"from\": 3559, \"to\": 3568}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic building spree\", \"from\": 3579, \"to\": 3605}]}, {\"sentence\": \"According to the CDES, construction and refurbishing companies expect to increase revenues by up to three billion euros from the Olympics.\", \"from\": 3628, \"to\": 3766, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the CDES\", \"from\": 3641, \"to\": 3649}, {\"ngram\": \"construction and refurbishing companies\", \"from\": 3651, \"to\": 3690}, {\"ngram\": \"revenues\", \"from\": 3710, \"to\": 3718}, {\"ngram\": \"up to three billion euros\", \"from\": 3722, \"to\": 3747}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 3753, \"to\": 3765}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tourism expects to earn up to 3.6 billion euros from the 15 million visitors predicted for the Games, including two million from abroad.\", \"from\": 3768, \"to\": 3904, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Tourism\", \"from\": 3768, \"to\": 3775}, {\"ngram\": \"up to 3.6 billion euros\", \"from\": 3792, \"to\": 3815}, {\"ngram\": \"the 15 million visitors\", \"from\": 3821, \"to\": 3844}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 3859, \"to\": 3868}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Oddo BHF predicted that media, leisure, drinks and alcohol, consumer goods and transport companies would all benefit from the Games.\", \"from\": 3906, \"to\": 4038, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Oddo BHF\", \"from\": 3906, \"to\": 3914}, {\"ngram\": \"media\", \"from\": 3930, \"to\": 3935}, {\"ngram\": \"leisure\", \"from\": 3937, \"to\": 3944}, {\"ngram\": \"drinks\", \"from\": 3946, \"to\": 3952}, {\"ngram\": \"alcohol\", \"from\": 3957, \"to\": 3964}, {\"ngram\": \"consumer goods and transport companies\", \"from\": 3966, \"to\": 4004}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 4028, \"to\": 4037}]}, {\"sentence\": \"HOUSE RULES\", \"from\": 4040, \"to\": 4051, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"HOUSE RULES\", \"from\": 4040, \"to\": 4051}]}]}"